Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.48,0:00:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Fuku-{\i1}chan{\i0}, what you're\Ntrying to tell me is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate poured into a form,\Nthen cooled and hardened isn't homemade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.78,0:00:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you won't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.15,0:00:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you're saying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.61,0:00:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... to put it plainly, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuku-{\i1}chan{\i0}, if that's the\Nway you feel about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next year, I'll slap you across the face
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with a masterpiece that\Nwill satisfy even you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaburaya Middle School
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:58.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You hold your breath to make it through\Nthe bewildering day that confronts you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:05.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know what this is, don't you?\NWhat do you want to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:11.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The pain from shrugging\Nit all off as nothing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.63,0:01:17.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}urges you on enough to be encouraging{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.55,0:01:24.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Catching hold but making a mess,\Nwe're still inadequate{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:32.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but as long as we can forge\Nour shining, unseen future selves...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:40.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Awaken and run where it takes you,\Nleaving mirages behind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:47.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Run with your desire to change,\Nfrom your comfort zone into freedom{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:54.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Start choosing between now\Nand the brilliance you can attain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:02:02.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unaware of your destination,\Ndeep breaths following shallow ones{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:13.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Case of the Homemade Chocolates
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just too hard to make chocolate\Nout of cocoa beans, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does look that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to make the greatest\Nhandmade chocolate there is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if Fuku-{\i1}chan {\i0}still has any complaints,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lock him up against a wall somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and read every last word\Nof this book to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if that's still not good enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cram the chocolate into his mouth!\NS-Stob!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayaka-{\i1}san{\i0}... I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's anything I can do\Nto help, please tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Chi-{\i1}chan{\i0}! Do you know of\Nany place that sells ingredients
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to fancy pastry shops and so forth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... There's a store\Nnext to the market
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that deals in ingredients\Nintended for professional use.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to show you where?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:02:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure that Fuku-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't hear anything from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, how about this Sunday?\NHave they forgotten I'm here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, show me where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Oreki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you say anything either, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'd appreciate it if you'd\Nstop glaring at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:18.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Game Center
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Satoshi's bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hotaro! Nice timing,\Npassing by here like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say to a game\Nfor old time's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's no reason\Nfor me to hurry home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been in here since middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the Viper II. Hotaro,\Nyou'll take the Raiden, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the only one I know how to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Area: Airport. Get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:04:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure he'd concentrate\Non evading, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this how Satoshi usually fights?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is clearly different.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi's play back when\Nwe were in middle school
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was focused only on winning as his goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He would do whatever it takes to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if he {\i1}did {\i0}lose, he didn't\Ntry to hide his frustration,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and was an awfully sore loser.\NCome on, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's switch places and go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he trying to draw me in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that was a good game!\NSuperb joystick action there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Hotaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there at the end, why did\Nyou charge in like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to robots, hand-to-hand\Nfighting is more adventurous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this is who Satoshi is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's changed since middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What good will it do to tense up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he will accept it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Chi-{\i1}chan{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is there anyone that {\i1}you {\i0}like?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Itchy... Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"This chocolate bar is a present to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Oreki Tomoe, trembling\Nwith 'sympathy.'"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:55.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki-{\i1}san{\i0}, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning. So tell me,\Nhow did Ibara's chocolate go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finished. But it was\Nquite a bit of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had to sample different\Nkinds of chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet she gobbled\Nthem up in no time flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's not nice, Oreki-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, as a result, she\Ncompleted her masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be what it means to put\None's whole heart into something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's she going to\Ndo with the chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, from what I heard, Mayaka-{\i1}san\N{\i0}can't get out of her Manga Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she's going to leave it\Nin the club room, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Satoshi will be thrilled\Nwith the whole production.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki-{\i1}san{\i0}, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today... is Valentine's Day...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my family, it's our practice not\Nto give year-end or summer gifts,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and as such, on Valentine's Day, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's supposed to snow today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, for real?\NI didn't bring an umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're going to be late, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:35.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Science Prep Room
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:47.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To Fuku-{\i1}chan{\i0}, please accept\Nthis Valentine's chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hotaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you on your way to the club room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, I'm waiting in the library\Nuntil either the sleet lets up,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or it turns to snow.\NIt's too cold in the club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to the club room?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, Ibara is stuck in\NManga Club and can't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Word travels fast. Chitanda-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With what, for heaven's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:26.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Science Prep Room
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:37.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Library
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Chitanda...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where Fukube-{\i1}san {\i0}is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I thought maybe\Nsomething had come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him around a half hour ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he said he was\Ngoing to the club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll wait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukube-{\i1}san {\i0}is taking his time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait! Something awful happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It finally stopped sleeting,\Nand I was about to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but tell me about it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but at least\Nhear what I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I carelessly left the room open,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and did the worst thing to Mayaka-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chocolate...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayaka-{\i1}san{\i0}'s chocolate...\Nhas been stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to see Ibara
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once she found out that her\Nchocolate had been stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I don't handle\Nthe horror genre very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:13.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A History of Hannya Masks
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:16.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Risshun {\i0}('Dawn of Spring')\NWhen the first signs of spring appear
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:16.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Oreki-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:27.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Freshly waxed\NNo entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like we can use\Nthe west stairs to the 4th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go up by the east stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:35.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Industrial Arts Club Graduation Exhibit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this look level to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A trapezoid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lowered it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was sitting right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heart-shaped, about this big,\Nin clear plastic wrapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty big.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was right here until I went\Nto go look for Fukube-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you return to the club room?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just after 5:00. If only\NI had taken the trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to lock the door during those 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chitanda-{\i1}san{\i0}, this isn't something\Nyou should beat yourself up over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm far more at fault\Nfor having been so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you told Ibara about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I haven't. Maybe it's cowardly of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't plan to do that until\NI've looked as much as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's nowhere in this room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Fukube-{\i1}san {\i0}and I searched\Nthe room and around the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran into her on the stairs, so we\Nboth came to the room together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. By the way, how long was\Nthat Industrial Arts guy there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Industrial Arts?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy with the glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy from the Industrial Arts Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was putting that poster up\Nwhen I went looking for Fukube-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect. If the Industrial Arts\Nguy was there the whole time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he might remember who came and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. Isn't it possible\Nthat he's the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. What kind of culprit hangs\Naround after stealing something,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:11:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,casually hanging up a poster?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People who have passed by here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were a total of three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three of them? W-What sort\Nof people were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they have any\Ndistinguishing characteristics?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the culprit\Nis still on the 4th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi, what clubs are\Nhere on the 4th floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it's the Classic Lit Club,\Nthe Light Music Club,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Astronomy Club,\Nand the Philosophy Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, I think that we\Nand the Astronomy Club
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are the only ones who\Nhaven't gone home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to say, this is unusual...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You getting into this like you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could start sleeting again, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be able to get it back now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would anyone do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start by exploring the possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:02.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Elective Classroom â™ª5
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? The Classic Lit Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please return our chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was something we needed\Nto ask you about, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As it happens, some Valentine's\Nchocolate was stolen from our room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're looking for any\Nwitnesses who saw anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate? I doubt we have\Nourselves a love bandit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see anyone up here\Nbetween 4:45 and 5:00?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only thing I thought\NI'd do here is fumble
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... We were pretty much\N in the swing of things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or take double damage. It's miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember the time, but\NNakayama and Yoshihara stepped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you let me replenish my items?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Oda might have left, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three out of the five, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anyone pack up and\Nget ready to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oda-{\i1}san {\i0}is the girl over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Nakayama! And let\Nme just say, Mr. Detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nobody came back in here\Nwith any chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! Did any of you get even\Na glimpse of anything chocolatey
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while you were in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, would you mind\Nnot rubbing it in, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could say I saw some.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got shut out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything else you wanted to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Senpai.\NI apologize for any disrespect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's get back to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too late, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawakiguchi-{\i1}san {\i0}was upset, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we must do whatever it takes\Nto get Mayaka-{\i1}san{\i0}'s chocolate back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hotaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's just go\Nback to the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time we wrapped this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any way to get to the\N4th floor other than that stairway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Realistically speaking, just the\Nstairway that was being waxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there were no traces of any use.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Come to think of it,\Ndid you check the girls' restroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think it's in the restroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance in a million.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A chance in a million isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can pretty well guess what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep your mouth shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, there's only one possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.77,0:15:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you all doing in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Maya...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how was it? My chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right down to business, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ibara...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mayaka-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left the room without locking the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the chocolate was\Nstolen while I was out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, is that right?\NIt was stolen, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayaka-{\i1}san{\i0}, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chi-{\i1}chan{\i0}, there's nothing\Nfor you to apologize about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it does kind of hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home now. Chi-{\i1}chan{\i0},\Nreally, don't let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please step aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to find that chocolate,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if I have to resort to\Nsomewhat forceful measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't, I won't be able\Nto face Mayaka-{\i1}san {\i0}tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive myself for what I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayaka-{\i1}san {\i0}was supposed to\Nhave a happy memory of today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say that I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not as easily moved as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But let me deal with this. There are\Nsome things I need to consider.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't do that while you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea who it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakayama, from the Astronomy Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ibara's chocolate was a\Npretty decent size, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you couldn't hide it\Nunder a boy's school uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might hide it on the inside,\Nbut it would make you move unnaturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with a sailor uniform,\Nyou could pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you strapped it to your leg,\Nyour skirt would hide it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will give Ibara's chocolate\Nto Satoshi within the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take this over,\Nwhile you relax and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will trust you, Oreki-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi, let me see your drawstring bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm giving Ibara's chocolate to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This fulfills my promise to Chitanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi was the one who\Nstole Ibara's chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nicely done, Hotaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment I heard that the\Nchocolate had been stolen,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking that the only one\Nwho would do such a thing was Satoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I became certain when we talked\Nto the Industrial Arts Club member.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi said "You lowered it too much."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he hadn't previously said\N"You should lower the right side,"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he wouldn't have responded\Nthe way he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi probably hid in the\N3rd floor boys' restroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,waiting for Chitanda to pass,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:10.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Science Prep Room
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then recovered\Nthe chocolate from the vacant club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was bigger than he expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't fit in his bag,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and there were no suitably\Nlarge bags in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he fled with it as-is,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and happened to bump into\NChitanda, he'd be called out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which meant that the action\NSatoshi took was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you even hesitate when you broke it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This makes us even.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last April, you concocted that tale\Nabout the Joro Spider Society
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that I could get away from Chitanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's right, I did.\NBut no one was hurt by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:19:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Except for you, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll at least explain to me\Nwhy you did it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you tell me it was all a joke...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have no choice but to pound you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For both Chitanda and Ibara, with my fists.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't want to get pounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not say. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm going to\Nhave to say anyway, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hotaro, do you think\NI'm the compulsive type?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you fixate on your interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where you'd be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People like that apply\Nthemselves to something,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and don't want anyone else in\Nthat field to get the better of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're not like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not. I'll never be\Nthe best person at anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to be more exact, I've...\Nstopped trying to be the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You felt something was out of place\Nat the game center, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About how I wasn't\Npreoccupied with winning?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old me wanted\Nto win for winning's sake,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and was fussier about a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was no fun, you know? Winning\Nafter focusing so hard on winning,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but not having any fun\Ndoing so, is hard to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have any fun\Nwinning, how fun can it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, one day, I just grew tired of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I became particular about\Nnot being particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I really have enjoyed\Nmyself more. Every day is happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there was one problem with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayaka is great. Really great.\NThere's no one else like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having Mayaka wanting to be\Nwith me is like a dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.07,0:21:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay for me to be\Npreoccupied with Mayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without a doubt,\NI want to be with Mayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want to be\Npreoccupied with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all about what {\i1}I {\i0}want. I'm not\Nthinking about how Mayaka feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.55,0:22:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, don't you think\Nthat's pretty self-centered?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't want to take\NMayaka for granted, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if I let go of my lighthearted\Nself and embrace Mayaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.60,0:22:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might go back to being my old self.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.40,0:22:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's something that terrifies me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.61,0:22:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you didn't accept it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.69,0:22:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. And now it's this year.\NBut I still haven't found my answer yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.62,0:22:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was the only way not to accept\Nchocolate that I couldn't accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.91,0:22:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you also ended up hurting Chitanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things don't go as smoothly\Nfor me as they do for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.75,0:22:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayaka and I didn't figure on Chitanda-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayaka-{\i1}san{\i0}! Please wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chi-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.51,0:22:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...\NI'm sorry, Chi-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually know who stole the chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:22:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:23:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, after last Valentine's Day,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told Fuku-{\i1}chan {\i0}that I would\Nwait until he found his answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.52,0:23:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today was my day to test if he had.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.36,0:23:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the chocolate was...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.15,0:23:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Fuku-{\i1}chan {\i0}probably has it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.37,0:23:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is... that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really am sorry that all this\Neffectively put one over on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. I'm the one who seemed\Nto blow it out of proportion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, when Oreki-{\i1}san {\i0}said that\Nthe Astronomy Club girl stole it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.30,0:23:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he was telling a white\Nlie to cover for Fuku-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.39,0:23:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how unkind of Fukube-{\i1}san{\i0}...\NPlaying along like it was stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.68,0:23:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That really is galling! But the\Nmost galling thing of all
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.06,0:23:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is myself, for still liking Fuku-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.98,0:23:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Chi-{\i1}chan{\i0}, let's go\Nout for cake, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.65,0:23:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.20,0:23:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Hotaro,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's everything I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.95,0:23:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.25,0:24:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't something we can tell Chitanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.38,0:24:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, huh? I'd rather get pounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.09,0:24:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, is your answer at least on the horizon?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.56,0:24:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think my answer will come soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.81,0:24:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.82,0:24:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For being as deft as you are,\Nyou sure are ham-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.24,0:24:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sorry, I didn't know\Nanything at all about you,"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.91,0:24:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,might have been something I\Nshould have told him, but I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.00,0:24:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I safely managed to get\Nthe chocolate back to Satoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.63,0:24:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right? That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.84,0:24:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, don't give it too much thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.09,0:24:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki-{\i1}san{\i0}, thanks for\Neverything you did today.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.85,0:25:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.73,0:25:08.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayaka
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.99,0:25:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.03,0:25:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.63,0:25:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.67,0:25:55.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This situation is an unscientific\Nmontage of emotions{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.34,0:25:59.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is calling whom?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.01,0:26:04.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your gaze darts away when I turn around\N(I can feel it){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.98,0:26:07.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's unkind to tell me I'm imagining things{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.23,0:26:12.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They say having antennas\Nis a talent, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.77,0:26:17.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I mean I want to know\N(I mean) (don't you?){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.85,0:26:24.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll turn up the heat on your youth\Nfor you now, while there's time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.64,0:26:29.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we can solve this tomorrow,\Nwhy not solve it right now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.31,0:26:34.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to solve your mystery{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.90,0:26:39.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Track down that secretive boyish figure!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.60,0:26:47.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(Today) you are a fantasy,\Ndrawing me to you, no fair!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.15,0:26:52.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My curiosity is expanding,\Nlack of tricks notwithstanding{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.81,0:26:59.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm fascinated, and I have to know, why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.02,0:27:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "The Doll That\NTook the Long Way Around."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.41,0:27:13.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Doll That Took the Long Way Around
